"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Conferences\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://yoast.com/?p=722940\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:326:\"Are you living in the San Francisco Bay Area or in Los Angeles (or surroundings)? And, are you planning to organize a WP Meetup this summer? Joost de Valk would love to come, visit and speak at your WP Meetup this summer! We (Joost and Marieke) will betraveling through California this summer. We&#8217;ll take our [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"Marieke van de Rakt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2022:\"<p>Are you living in the San Francisco Bay Area or in Los Angeles (or surroundings)? And, are you planning to organize a WP Meetup this summer? <a href=\"https://yoast.com/about-us/joost-de-valk/\">Joost de Valk</a> would love to come, visit and speak at your WP Meetup this summer!</p>\n<p><img class=\"noborder alignnone wp-image-726593 size-full\" src=\"https://yoast-mercury.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2016/05/MariekeJoost_USA.png\" alt=\"Marieke and Joost of Yoast visit the US\" width=\"1200\" height=\"628\" srcset=\"https://yoast-mercury.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2016/05/MariekeJoost_USA.png 1200w, https://yoast-mercury.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2016/05/MariekeJoost_USA-250x131.png 250w, https://yoast-mercury.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2016/05/MariekeJoost_USA-768x402.png 768w, https://yoast-mercury.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2016/05/MariekeJoost_USA-600x314.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></p>\n<p>We (<a href=\"https://yoast.com/about-us/joost-de-valk/\">Joost</a> and <a href=\"https://yoast.com/about-us/marieke-van-de-rakt/\">Marieke</a>) will betraveling through California this summer. We&#8217;ll take our four children (aged 10, 6, 4 and 1) along with us. It will be mostly fun, sightseeing and vacation, but we&#8217;d love to do some Meetups in California as well. So, please let us know if you&#8217;d like Joost de Valk to come to your Meetup!</p>\n<h2>Our timetable</h2>\n<p>What are the possibilities? From July 23 until July 29 we&#8217;ll stay in San Fransisco. Anything within an hour&#8217;s (or 90 minute) drive is doable!</p>\n<p>After July 29, we&#8217;ll be off the radar, doing some serious sightseeing. We&#8217;ll be in Los Angeles (well, Carlsbad to be precise) from August 12 to August 19.</p>\n<p>Please <a href=\"mailto:marketing@yoast.com\">contact us</a> if you would like to have Joost de Valk come to your Meetup. Hope to see you soon!</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><a href=\"https://vimeo.com/140533382\">Check out this video to see Joost present at WordCamp NL!</a></span></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://yoast.com/joost-marieke-visit-california-summer/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\