(5703,	41,	'wpcf-features',	'<h2>Condensation type industrial dehumidifiers and dryers</h2>\r\n<p>The lowest capacity model in this portable series of condensation dehumidifier is 32 litre / 24 hours and the highest capacity model is 300 litre/ 24 hour.</p>\r\n<h2>Model TTK 125S commercial dehumidifier</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/TTK655-condensation-dehumidifier.png\"><img src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/TTK655-condensation-dehumidifier.png\" alt=\"TTK655 Condensation Dehumidifier-vacker global\" width=\"351\" height=\"264\" align=\"right\" size-full wp-image-925\" /></a><p>This model is the smallest in this series.</p>\r\n<p>Technical details:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dehumidification performance : 32 litres per 24 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Operating range temperature: 5- 32C /32 to 100 % RH</li>\r\n	<li>Air flow rate: 300 m/h</li>\r\n	<li>Weight:24 kg</li>\r\n	<li>Dimension : 375 mm (L) x 375mm (W) x 603mm (H)</li>\r\n	<li>Electrical consumption : 0.56 kW</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Model TTK 800 industrial dryer</h2>\r\n<p>This is condensation type industrial dryer of TTK Pro series</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dehumidification performance : 150litres per 24 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Operating range temperature: 5- 32C /32 to 100 % RH</li>\r\n	<li>Air flow rate: 950 m/h</li>\r\n	<li>Weight:70kg</li>\r\n	<li>Dimension : 585 mm (L) x 630mm (W) x 1020mm (H)</li>\r\n	<li>Electrical consumption : 2.4kW</li>\r\n	<li>Compressor type :Rotary piston compressor</li>\r\n	<li>Type of cooling agent : R-407C</li>\r\n	<li>Sound level at meter : 63 dB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Optional water pump is available for all the models for pumping water to longer distance if required.</p>\r\n<h2>TTK 655 S Commercial Dehumidifier</h2>\r\n<p>This is the model of commercial dehumidifier with the highest capacity</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dehumidification performance : 150litres per 24 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Operating range temperature: 5- 32C /32 to 100 % RH</li>\r\n	<li>Air flow rate: 1500 m/h</li>\r\n	<li>Weight:70kg</li>\r\n	<li>Dimension : 585 mm (L) x 630mm (W) x 1020mm (H)</li>\r\n	<li>Electrical consumption : 2.4kW</li>\r\n	<li>Compressor type :Rotary piston compressor</li>\r\n	<li>Type of cooling agent : R-407C</li>\r\n	<li>Sound level at meter : 63 dB</li>\r\n</ul>'),
