(6410,	25,	'wpcf-features',	'<h2>iMini series Temperature &amp; Humidity data logger</h2>\r\n<p> iMini series is the most popular and economic series of data loggers. iMini series has two range of products viz. Temperature only data loggers and Temperature + Humidity data loggers</p>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/humidity-data-logger-external-sensor.png\"><img src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/humidity-data-logger-external-sensor.png\" alt=\"Humidity Datalogger External Sensor-vacker global\" width=\"351\" height=\"264\" align=\"right\" size-full wp-image-970\" /></a><h2>Features of iMini Temperature and Humidity data logger by Cryopak, USA</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Memory capacity : 16000 readings to 128000 readings</li>\r\n	<li>Temperature Sensor type : Internal and/or external</li>\r\n	<li>HumiditySensor type : External</li>\r\n	<li>4 visual alarms  2 on the higher side and 2 on the lower side.Indicated by LED of different colours</li>\r\n	<li>programmable sampling interval from 5 seconds to 17 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Temperature measurement range :-40 C to +80 C (-40 F to +176 F)</li>\r\n	<li>For application such as refrigerators, a gycol bottle can be used optionally to reduce sudden fluctuations due to frequent door openings.</li>\r\n	<li>Warranty : 2 years</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The following models are available in this series of temperature &amp; humidity data logger:</p>\r\n<h2>Model no. MX-HE-S-16-L</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: Temperature andHumidity Multi-use data logger with external sensor;</li>\r\n	<li>of sensor :3 nos;2 Internal &amp;1 External senor (1 no internal temperature sensor, 1 no. external temperature sensor, 1 no. internal humidity senor)</li>\r\n	<li>Type of sensors : Digital sensor&amp; NTC</li>\r\n	<li>Memory capacity : 16000 readings (higher models with capacity upto 128,000 readings are available)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Model No. MX-HS-S-16-L</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: Temperature &amp; Humidity Multi-use data logger with internal sensor;</li>\r\n	<li>of sensor : 2nos; 1 no internal temperature sensor, 1 no. internal humidity sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Type of sensors : Digital sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Memory capacity : 16000 readings (higher models with capacity upto 128,000 readings are available)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Also please check ourinstruction videos and manuals of iMini series data loggers</p>\r\n<h2>iLog series Temperature and Humidity data loggers</h2>\r\n<p>This series hasmore sophisticated models for environments which require high precision data logging</p>\r\n<h2>Features of iLogTemperature &amp; Humidity data logger by Cryopak, USA</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Memory capacity of 32,000 readings</li>\r\n	<li>LCD display with capability to view different functions</li>\r\n	<li>Visual and audible alarms</li>\r\n	<li>Capability to bookmark times</li>\r\n	<li>Very wide temperature range of measurement</li>\r\n	<li>Accuracy of 0.35 C</li>\r\n	<li>Detachable, customizable external sensor lengths and probe styles</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Model no.EI-HS-D-32-L</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: Temperature andHumidity Multi-use data logger</li>\r\n	<li>Measuring range :-40 to +70C (-40 to +158 F)</li>\r\n	<li>of sensors : 2nos; 1 no internal temperature sensor, 1 no. internal humidity sensor</li>\r\n	<li>LCD Operating Range:-20 C to +70 C (-4 F to +158 F)</li>\r\n	<li>Program Interval: 5 seconds to 10 days</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution 0.1 C / 0.1 F / 0.1%</li>\r\n	<li>Battery Life 1-2 years (depending on usage)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
