(8909,	5,	'wpcf-mission-vision',	'<h1>Our commitment</h1><p>We are committed in delivering our products and services with a touch of topmost quality. We understand the value and importance of quality in all walks of life and we strive to maintain the same in every country and every area of our operations.</p><p>It is our promise that every customer will receive only quality products and services from any of our group companies anywhere in the world.</p><h2>Vision</h2><p>Our vision is to become a dependable partner for our customers in the entire Middle East in the following segments:</p><h3>a. Temperature &amp; Humidity management</h3><h3>b. Cold Chain Management</h3><h3>c. Automation</h3><h3>d. Supply of sensors &amp; solutions</h3><h1>Mission</h1><p>The mission of Team Vacker is to provide a single point design, supply and installation of leading edge reliable technology aimed at latest technical solutions for engineering projects.</p><h2>This shall be achieved through :-</h2><h3>Employees</h3><p>Trained, Innovative, customer centric team of professionals who would develop innovative solutions for the customer. Vacker shall have a performance oriented team and a corporate culture based on mutual respect, trust and personal freedom. Vacker shall provide a work environment that creates and fosters a spirit of Teamwork, Creativity, Mutual Trust for our employees</p><h3>Products</h3><p>Solutions for the future. Work constantly on continual improvement to give the customers the latest in technology and partner with the best in industry. Vacker shall be engaged in engineering solutions for its customers in residential and commercial segments and supplies of electrical, mechanical and civil accessories for all segments of customers including industrial, infrastructure and marine segments.</p><h3>Customer Service</h3><p>Vacker shall provide tailor made solutions of world class quality to achieve economical energy management, thus ensuring sustainable energy solutions and shall be fully committed to improving the level of service that it provides for all its customers. It is committed to good customer care and recognizes that every member of staff has an important role to play in responding positively to the needs and expectations of its customers.</p><h3>Partners</h3><p>Vacker shall strive to maintain a mutually beneficial working relationship.</p><h3>Corporate Social Responsibility</h3><p>Vacker will carry out operations in an environmentally and socially responsible manner. We understand that highest ethical and moral standards are necessary for the foundation of good business establishments, and we will operate without compromising ethical business practices and integrity.</p>'),
