(8915,	5,	'wpcf-our-team',	'<h1>Our Team</h1><p>The company is lead by Chief Executive Officer Mr. Dileep PS, who is an electrical engineering professional with varied experience in different countries including multinational companies. His experience includes design and execution of projects, project management, design and manufacture of HV &amp; LV Switchgear, Automation etc. He is certified in various automation protocols and is a certified KNX partner as well. Also he is a certified ISO External auditor and has successfully implemented ISO system in couple of organizations.</p><p>Team members in each country consist of a country head and project professionals as per the requirement of each country. The design activities for all countries are mainly centralized at the head office at Dubai and the team mainly consists of qualified professionals in Electrical, Mechanical and Automation disciplines. The team at Dubai is supported by AutoCAD draughtsman.</p><p>The company operates under a common set of quality guidelines and qualified personnel in each country ensure highest level of quality in all areas of operation.</p>'),
(8916,	5,	'wpcf-quality-policy',	'<h1>Quality Policy</h1><p><strong>Vacker Global Group</strong> is committed to achieving topmost quality in all their services in every country of operation. We will ensure to provide products and services of excellent quality on time to the customers. This shall be achieved through our operations based on written procedures in line with ISO 9001:2008 and latest relevant standards.</p><h2>The key areas of focus are:</h2><h3>Customer Satisfaction</h3><p>Customer satisfaction is the most important factor for our success and we will offer only high quality products and services to our customers.</p><h3>Employee Responsibility</h3><p>All of our employees will take their best possible efforts to achieve highest quality standards in all the products and services offered by us.</p><h3>Continuous Improvement</h3><p>We will constantly collect feedback from our customers and suppliers based on which will take our best efforts to continuously improve the quality of our products and services.</p><h3>Employee performance</h3><p>We will provide safe and healthy working conditions to all our employees and continuous training in the right areas will be provided to enhance their performance.</p>'),
