(5,	1,	'2015-05-27 15:36:39',	'2015-05-27 15:36:39',	'<p><strong>Vacker Global group of companies</strong> is specialized in providing suitable engineering solutions with energy conservation being the key objective.</p><p>We deal with Industrial/Process automation, Home/Office automation, MEP contracting, trading in Electro-Mechanical items and engineering activities. Our services and products range through a variety of sectors such as Cold Chain Management, Data Loggers, Automation, Food safety and HACCP, Dehumidifier and Humidifier.</p><p>Customer satisfaction, ethics and integrity are of utmost value to us, which has resulted in Vacker Global being successful in maintaining its core values.</p><p>Vacker Global, currently operates in five countries, UAE, Kuwait, Oman, USA and India. In Saudi Arabia/ KSA we cater to areas such as Riyadh, Dammam, Jeddah, Al Khobar etc.</p><p>Please see our Profile here: <a title=\"Vacker Global Profile\" href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Vacker-Global-Profile.pdf\">View - </a><a title=\"Vacker Global Profile\" href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Vacker-Global-Profile.pdf\" download=\"\">Download</a></p>',	'About Us',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'about-us',	'',	'',	'2016-04-25 12:38:10',	'2016-04-25 12:38:10',	'',	0,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/?page_id=5',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
