(11,	1,	'2015-05-27 15:37:52',	'2015-05-27 15:37:52',	'<p>Vacker Global is an established group of companies offering a variety of services and products in sectors ranging from Cold Chain Management, Automation, Data Loggers, Dehumidifier and Humidifier, and Food safety and HACCP.</p><p>With energy conservation being our main objective, we deal in areas such as Industrial/Process automation, Home/Office automation, engineering activities, MEP contracting and trading in Electro-Mechanical items.</p><p>Our company offers services in Saudi Arabia or KSA areas such as Riyadh, Jeddah, Dammam, Al Khobar etc.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Have an enquiry?</p><p>Reach us out by filling in the form below and we shall get back to you.</p><h1>ENQUIRY</h1><p>[contact-form-7 id=\"67\" title=\"Contact form 1\"]</p>',	'Contact Us',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'contact-us',	'',	'',	'2016-05-02 14:08:28',	'2016-05-02 14:08:28',	'',	0,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/?page_id=11',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
