(15,	1,	'2015-05-28 14:03:24',	'2015-05-28 14:03:24',	'<h1>Working at Vacker Global</h1><h2>Why Vacker Global Group?</h2><p>Vacker Global Group of companies has carved its niche in the field of automation, for over five years, offering a wide range of custom engineering solutions. In Saudi Arabia or KSA, we cater to areas like Al Khobar, Riyadh, Dammam, Jeddah, etc.</p><p>Team work, we believe, is essential for growth and we train our employees to further hone their talent, thereby benefitting the individual and the company as a whole.</p><h2>Life at Vacker Global Group</h2><p>Each one of us is blessed with one or more intrinsic talent(s) that needs to be nurtured the right way. We at Vacker Global, understand just that and hence encourage our employees to develop their skills by owning and enjoying responsibilities in their respective areas of operations, without following any hierarchical multilevel structure. An amiable work culture in addition to a skilled and cooperative workforce is our forte.</p><p>We offer legions of opportunities in various countries to those who wish to enhance their potential and discover their innate talent.</p><p>Begin a prolific career by sending your resume to our <a href=\"mailto:career.ksa@vackerglobal.com\">Career team</a>.</p>',	'Careers',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'careers',	'',	'',	'2016-04-25 12:49:58',	'2016-04-25 12:49:58',	'',	0,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/?page_id=15',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
