(204,	1,	'2015-06-02 06:54:49',	'2015-06-02 06:54:49',	'<div class=\"post-entry\">\r\n<p>These type is also known as adsorption type dehumidifiers. The technology used in these models&nbsp;is absorbing the moisture content using&nbsp;an adsorbent such as silica gel.</p>\r\n<h2>Desiccant Industrial dehumidifier mobile</h2>\r\n<p>These are portable dehumidifiers for industrial and commercial applications. Even though portable, these are available upto a capacity of 1.0 kg/h and 200 cubic meter/hour. Few of the models are listed here:</p>\r\n<h3>Lightweight model TTR 200<a href=\"http://temperaturemonitoring.vackerllc.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/portable-industrial-dehumidifier.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-3078\" src=\"http://temperaturemonitoring.vackerllc.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/portable-industrial-dehumidifier-284x300.jpg\" alt=\"portable-industrial-dehumidifier\" width=\"265\" height=\"279\"></a></h3>\r\n<p>These are very light weight and portable models and are the smallest in the desiccant series. These are equipped with electronic volume control which functions automatically based on the requirement of dry air. A hygrostat controls the machine for setting desired levels of humidity.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Operating range: 0 to 100% RH. / -15 C to +35 C</li>\r\n<li>performance of dehumidification: 0.35 kg/h</li>\r\n<li>Air flow rate: 40  120m/h</li>\r\n<li>Easy replacement of filter without dismantling the equipment</li>\r\n<li>Typical applications will be small warehouses, cold rooms etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Total weight is only 9 kg which makes it easy for handling and relocating.</p>\r\n<p>A hose can be connected for air&nbsp;output.</p>\r\n<p>Other&nbsp;models in this series are TTR 300,&nbsp;TTR 400,TTR &nbsp;D,&nbsp;TTR 500 D &amp;&nbsp;TTR 160</p>\r\n<h3>Stainless Steel model TTR 250 HP or marine application<a href=\"http://temperaturemonitoring.vackerllc.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/dehumidifier-for-marine-application.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-3014\" src=\"http://temperaturemonitoring.vackerllc.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/dehumidifier-for-marine-application-201x300.jpg\" alt=\"dehumidifier-for-marine-application\" width=\"201\" height=\"300\"></a></h3>\r\n<p>This model of desiccant dehumidifier is fitted with a radial fan and an additional motor to pump air over long distances. This makes it ideal&nbsp;applications in ship and other marine environments. Marine dehumidifiers require to perform in harsh environments.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Operating range: 0 to 100% RH. / -20 C to +35 C</li>\r\n<li>performance of dehumidification: 1&nbsp;kg/h</li>\r\n<li>Air flow rate: 40  120m/h</li>\r\n<li>Nominal air volume: 100 m/h</li>\r\n<li>Easy replacement of filter without dismantling the equipment</li>\r\n<li>Typical applications will be small warehouses, cold rooms etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The air flow over long distance can be connected either to the intake moist air or dry air output simply by changing the internal hose connection. The marine dehumidifier can connect to long distance of flexible hose so that the processed air can be taken to longer distances.</p>\r\n<p>Other models in stainless steel models are&nbsp;&nbsp;TTR 250 &amp; TTR 250Ex</p>\r\n<h3>Stainless Steel Explosion Proof model TTR 250 Ex<a href=\"http://temperaturemonitoring.vackerllc.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/explosion-proof-dehumidifiers.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-3021\" src=\"http://temperaturemonitoring.vackerllc.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/explosion-proof-dehumidifiers-251x300.jpg\" alt=\"explosion-proof-dehumidifiers\" width=\"194\" height=\"231\"></a></h3>\r\n<p>This model&nbsp;of desiccant dehumidifier is for explosion proof environment and the model complies to Ex protection class ATEX zone 22 (Ex II 3D Ex c T240 C) .</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Operating range: 0 to 100% RH. / -20 C to +35 C</li>\r\n<li>Air flow rate: 180 m/h</li>\r\n<li>Dehumidification capacity: 1.1 kg/h</li>\r\n<li>Weight : 21 kg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Other types of dehumidifiers:</h2>\r\n<p>Please click the following links for other types of dehumidifiers by Trotec, Germany</p>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Dehumidifiers home page\" href=\"http://www.temperaturemonitoringuae.com/products/dehumidifiers/\">Dehumidifiers  Home Page</a></h3>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Stationary desiccant dehumidifiers\" href=\"http://www.temperaturemonitoringuae.com/products/dehumidifiers/desiccant-industrial-dehumidifier-stationary/\">Desiccant dehumidifiers&nbsp;stationary</a></h3>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Portable condensation dehumidifiers\" href=\"http://www.temperaturemonitoringuae.com/products/dehumidifiers/condensation-dehumidifier-portable/\">Condensation&nbsp;dehumidifiers portable</a><a title=\"Portble Desiccant dehumidifiers\" href=\"http://www.temperaturemonitoringuae.com/products/dehumidifiers/desiccant-industrial-dehumidifiers-portable/\"><br>\r\n</a></h3>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Stationary Condensation dehumidifiers \" href=\"http://www.temperaturemonitoringuae.com/products/dehumidifiers/condensation-dehumidifiers-stationary/\">Condensation&nbsp;dehumidifiers&nbsp;stationary</a></h3>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Dehumidifiers for home and office use\" href=\"http://www.temperaturemonitoringuae.com/products/dehumidifiers/dehumidifier-home-office/\">Dehumidifiers for home and office</a></h3>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Dehumidifiers for swimming pools\" href=\"http://www.temperaturemonitoringuae.com/products/dehumidifiers/dehumidifiers-for-swimming-pools/\">Condensation&nbsp;dehumidifiers&nbsp;for Swimming pools</a></h3>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Humidifier for increasing humidity\" href=\"http://www.temperaturemonitoringuae.com/products/dehumidifiers/humidifier-for-increasing-humidity/\">Humidifier for increasing humidity</a></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n									</div>',	'Dessicant Dehumidifier',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'39-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-06-02 06:5