(212,	1,	'2015-06-02 07:21:25',	'2015-06-02 07:21:25',	'\r\n<p>Temperature and Humidity data loggers manufactured by Cryopak USA have wide variety of models for different range of temperature and humidity and different memory ranges. One of the major uses of these data loggers are for health care logistics. There are numerous models with internal and external sensors for temperature.</p>\r\n',	'Humidity Data Logger',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'25-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-06-02 07:21:25',	'2015-06-02 07:21:25',	'',	25,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/25-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(213,	1,	'2015-06-02 07:32:06',	'2015-06-02 07:32:06',	'<p>AccsenseElectrocorderdataloggers are electrical logging devices monitoring power/energy, current/voltage, power quality and more. These products perform ongoing datalogging to identify issues with supply and equipment; to calculate and prove the value of future energy savings; and as low-cost investments for long-term energy savings. Electrocorder constantly samples every cycle multiple times (recording the Min, Max and Average) over the set period. Additionally, specialized Electrosoft software is included FREE with every unit to assist with data interpretation, enabling users to define the voltage to plot power and energy, then simply upload their recorded data via USB to a PC for analysis.</p>',	'Electrical data loggers',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'electrical-data-loggers-kenya',	'',	'',	'2016-05-25 07:36:46',	'2016-05-25 07:36:46',	'',	0,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/?p=213',	0,	'post',	'',	0),
