(233,	1,	'2015-06-02 08:22:51',	'2015-06-02 08:22:51',	'\r\n<div class=\"post-entry\">\r\n<p>Condensation dehumidifier work on the principle of condensation of moisture from the surrounding air. Air is taken intothe dehumidifier through inletof the machine. The same is condensated inside the machine utilizing a compressor. The moisture content of the air is converted into water and dry air is pumped out. The machine produces water which willbe drained out automatically.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n',	'Condensation Dehumidifier',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'41-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-06-02 08:22:51',	'2015-06-02 08:22:51',	'',	41,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/41-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
