(298,	1,	'2015-06-03 18:28:58',	'2015-06-03 18:28:58',	'\r\n<p>Dehumidifiers are used for decreasing humidity levels of homes, offices, museums, warehouses, cold rooms etc. The operational principle is by absorbing the moisture from the air and thus reducing the levels. We are representing Trotec, Germany for their numerous dehumidifiers for industrial, commercial and residential applications. These are typically used for hotels, swimming pools, offices, warehouses, cold rooms, apartments, villa etc.</p>\r\n',	'Dehumidifier & Humidifier',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'55-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-06-03 18:28:58',	'2015-06-03 18:28:58',	'',	55,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/55-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(300,	1,	'2015-06-07 07:19:06',	'2015-06-07 07:19:06',	'\n<p>4 nos. existing class rooms at Indian Community School , Kuwait were converted into sophisticated laboratories (Chemistry, Biology, Physics &amp; Computer labs). The labs were completed in a record time of 45 days.</p>\n<h1>The labs have the following automated features for energy conservation:</h1>\n<ul>\n	<li>Light, Fan, AC etc. are automated to work only when children are present in the room.</li>\n	<li>The AC of computer lab is automated so that when students are not present, ACs will work alternatively for 12 hours each to keep the temperature under control. When students are present both ACs will work simultaneously to maintain the room temperature.</li>\n	<li>Gas leakage is automatically detected and the system shuts off in case of a leakage.</li>\n	<li>Even If the children leave the room with the burners in ON condition, gas will be shut OFF after everyone leaves the room.</li>\n</ul>\n',	'Sophisticated new academic Laboratories done for a School at Kuwait',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'77-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-06-07 07:19:06',	'2015-06-07 07:19:06',	'',	77,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/77-autosave-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(302,	1,	'2015-06-07 07:21:43',	'2015-06-07 07:21:43',	'\n<p>The temperature of the medicine storage room has to be maintained between 2 -8 Deg Celsius. Our system recently installed at a storage facility in Kuwait continuously monitors and records the temperature of the room. In case the temperature goes below 2 Deg Celsius or goes above 8 Deg Celsius for 5 minutes (the duration and the temperature range can be changed), an automated phone call is made up to 4 operators to inform the alarm condition. The phone calls are repeated until one of them attends and acknowledges the phone. The data can be stored in a computer and can be viewed through internet also from any part of the world.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n',	'Temperature monitoring & Alarm device installed at a medicine storage cold room',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'76-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-06-07 07:21:43',	'2015-06-07 07:21:43',	'',	76,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/76-autosave-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(303,	1,	'2015-06-07 07:26:19',	'2015-06-07 07:26:19',	'\n<p class=\"text-para\">A software will be installed on the mobile phone which will continuously check and transmit various parameters of the vehicle. The present day systems involve fixing a device in the car which is completely eliminated in our system. We need just to install the software on any compatible mobile phone and the data can be viewed either on the mobile or through the website. The charges involve just one time charges and very nominal yearly charges for the server space. Salient features are:</p>\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>Features accessible through Mobile App</li>\n	<li>Live Tracking</li>\n	<li>Replay</li>\n	<li>Transit Report</li>\n	<li>Features Accessible through Web</li>\n	<li>\n<p class=\"text-para text-para1\">Access control</p></li>\n	<li>\n<p class=\"text-para text-para1\">Report</p></li>\n	<li>\n<p class=\"text-para text-para1\">Supported Platforms for Mobile Apps</p></li>\n	<li>\n<p class=\"text-para text-para1\">Analytics</p></li>\n	<li>\n<p class=\"text-para text-para1\">Android version 2.2<br />Symbian 3</p></li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n',	'Vehicle tracking through the mobile phone of the driver',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'75-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-06-07 07:26:19',	'2015-06-07 07:26:19',	'',	75,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/75-autosave-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(305,	1,	'2015-06-07 07:36:45',	'2015-06-07 07:36:45',	'\r\n<p class=\"text-para\">The Hybrid Security Management Solutions being offered by DEVENIO-IS has the unique advantage that existing hardware need not be replaced and the solutions can be easily integrated into existing security surveillance cameras and access control systems. Few of the prominent capabilities are</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Integration with various cameras such as IR, thermal, Analogue, HD, IP etc</li>\r\n	<li>People and vehicles counting</li>\r\n	<li>Unattended object detection</li>\r\n	<li>Queue length detection</li>\r\n	<li>Intrusion detection which can exclude dogs, birds etc</li>\r\n	<li>No need to change existing hardware</li>\r\n	<li>Integrate thousands of cameras</li>\r\n	<li>Incorporate access control, fire detection or burglar alarm systems etc. into single software</li>\r\n	<li>Record and store any number plate of a vehicle entering or leaving</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',	'Vacker Group becomes dealer of Devenio IS in UAE, Kuwait, Oman & India for their Hybrid Security Management Systems Software',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'vacker-group-becomes-dealer-of-devenio-is-in-uae-kuwait-oman-india-for-their-hybrid-security-management-systems-software',	'',	'',	'2015-06-07 07:36:45',	'2015-06-07 07:36:45',	'',	0,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/?post_type=news-post&#038;p=305',	0,	'news-post',	'',	0),
(307,	1,	'2015-06-07 07:41:12',	'2015-06-07 07:41:12',	'<p class=\"text-para\">We have installed a complete solution to monitor all possible parameters of a data center and in case any of the parameters exceed the defined limits, a phone call will be made to 4 technicians and a voice mail will be delivered indicating the nature of the fault. Also SMS and emails will be sent simultaneously. The various parameters monitored are:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"twolink\">\r\n	<li>Temperature</li>\r\n	<li>Humidity</li>\r\n	<li>Air Flow</li>\r\n	<li>Water Leaks</li>\r\n	<li>Status of all doors of racks</li>\r\n	<li>Main Door Status</li>\r\n	<li>Power Failure</li>\r\n	<li>Excess Ampere</li>\r\n	<li>Excess Ampere</li>\r\n	<li>Voltage monitoring</li>\r\n	<li>Battery Condition</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"text-para\">All the above parameters will be continuously monitored and recorded in a central computer. A qualified technician was stationed round the clock in the data center. However after installing our integrated solution, the technician is not required and the system is working as expected for past 3 months.</p>\r\n',	'Data Centre Monitoring Project done in kuwait',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'data-centre-monitoring-project-done-in-kuwait',	'',	'',	'2015-08-27 16:08:02',	'2015-08-27 16:08:02',	'',	0,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/?post_type=news-post&#038;p=307',	0,	'news-post',	'',	0),
(308,	1,	'2015-06-07 07:42:24',	'2015-06-07 07:42:24',	'\r\n<p class=\"text-para\">We have carried out a temperature mapping &amp; validation of a massive pharmaceutical warehouse in Uae. The warehouse is more than 200,000 sq. ft in size and is having hundreds of racks. Even though theoretically we can carry out mapping on part by part basis, it will not give exact details in view of various operating conditions. Hence we took data simultaneously using hundreds of data loggers simultaneously and was validated through our international partners.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-para\">A complete 3D imaging also is done so as to carry out the once again during winter.</p>\r\n',	'Temperature mapping of warehouse done in UAE',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'temperature-mapping-of-warehouse-done-in-uae',	'',	'',	'2015-06-07 07:42:24',	'2015-06-07 07:42:24',	'',	0,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/?post_type=news-post&#038;p=308',	0,	'news-post',	'',	0),
