(420,	1,	'2015-08-27 17:10:33',	'2015-08-27 17:10:33',	'<p>4 nos. existing class rooms at Indian Community School , Kuwait were converted into sophisticated laboratories (Chemistry, Biology, Physics &amp; Computer labs). The labs were completed in a record time of 45 days.</p><h1>The labs have the following automated features for energy conservation:</h1><ul><li>Light, Fan, AC etc. are automated to work only when children are present in the room.</li><li>The AC of computer lab is automated so that when students are not present, ACs will work alternatively for 12 hours each to keep the temperature under control. When students are present both ACs will work simultaneously to maintain the room temperature.</li><li>Gas leakage is automatically detected and the system shuts off in case of a leakage.</li><li>Even If the children leave the room with the burners in ON condition, gas will be shut OFF after everyone leaves the room.</li></ul>',	'Sophisticated new academic Laboratories done for a School at Kuwait',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'sophisticated-new-academic-laboratories-done-for-a-school-at-kuwait',	'',	'',	'2016-04-25 13:14:22',	'2016-04-25 13:14:22',	'',	0,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/?p=420',	0,	'post',	'',	0),
(421,	1,	'2015-08-27 17:10:33',	'2015-08-27 17:10:33',	'<p>4 nos. existing class rooms at Indian Community School , Kuwait were converted into sophisticated laboratories (Chemistry, Biology, Physics &amp; Computer labs). The labs were completed in a record time of 45 days.</p>\r\n<h1>The labs have the following automated features for energy conservation:</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Light, Fan, AC etc. are automated to work only when children are present in the room.</li>\r\n	<li>The AC of computer lab is automated so that when students are not present, ACs will work alternatively for 12 hours each to keep the temperature under control. When students are present both ACs will work simultaneously to maintain the room temperature.</li>\r\n	<li>Gas leakage is automatically detected and the system shuts off in case of a leakage.</li>\r\n	<li>Even If the children leave the room with the burners in ON condition, gas will be shut OFF after everyone leaves the room.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',	'Sophisticated new academic Laboratories done for a School at Kuwait',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'420-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-08-27 17:10:33',	'2015-08-27 17:10:33',	'',	420,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/420-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(422,	1,	'2015-08-27 17:17:27',	'2015-08-27 17:17:27',	'<p>The temperature of the medicine storage room has to be maintained between 2 -8 Deg Celsius. Our system recently installed at a storage facility in Kuwait continuously monitors and records the temperature of the room. In case the temperature goes below 2 Deg Celsius or goes above 8 Deg Celsius for 5 minutes (the duration and the temperature range can be changed), an automated phone call is made up to 4 operators to inform the alarm condition. The phone calls are repeated until one of them attends and acknowledges the phone. The data can be stored in a computer and can be viewed through internet also from any part of the world.</p><h2>These instruments can be fitted for any temperature controlled rooms such as Blood Storage Rooms, Food Storage rooms etc.</h2>',	'Temperature monitoring & Alarm device installed at a medicine storage cold room',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'temperature-monitoring-alarm-device-installed-at-a-medicine-storage-cold-room',	'',	'',	'2016-04-25 13:15:27',	'2016-04-25 13:15:27',	'',	0,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/?p=422',	0,	'post',	'',	0),
