(424,	1,	'2015-08-27 17:21:09',	'2015-08-27 17:21:09',	'<p class=\"text-para\">A software will be installed on the mobile phone which will continuously check and transmit various parameters of the vehicle. The present day systems involve fixing a device in the car which is completely eliminated in our system. We need just to install the software on any compatible mobile phone and the data can be viewed either on the mobile or through the website. The charges involve just one time charges and very nominal yearly charges for the server space. Salient features are:</p><ul><li>Features accessible through Mobile App</li><li>Live Tracking</li><li>Replay</li><li>Transit Report</li><li>Features Accessible through Web</li><li>Access control</li><li>Report</li><li>Supported Platforms for Mobile</li><li>Analytics</li><li>Android version 2.2</li><li>Symbian 3</li></ul>',	'Vehicle tracking through the mobile phone of the driver',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'vehicle-tracking-through-the-mobile-phone-of-the-driver',	'',	'',	'2016-04-25 13:13:46',	'2016-04-25 13:13:46',	'',	0,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/?p=424',	0,	'post',	'',	0),
