(698,	1,	'2016-01-03 06:03:33',	'2016-01-03 06:03:33',	'<p> For a warehouse used for storage of sensitive goods, humidity is important. If you have to reduce humidity in a warehouse, you will need a <b> commercial dehumidifier. </b> The problem might be severe especially if the area is temperature controlled.</p> \r\n<p>Medicine warehouse, chemical warehouse, tobacco warehouse, cloth warehouse etc. are especially sensitive. Suppose the outside air is humid and the warehouse is at a lower temperature. In this case, condensation happens inside the warehouse. Thus warehouse attracts humidity from outside air. This increases humidity inside the area.</p>',	'Commercial Dehumidifier',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'525-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-01-03 06:03:33',	'2016-01-03 06:03:33',	'',	525,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/525-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
