al data logger can be connected if youwsant to record data.</li>\r\n	<li>Visual and audible alarms if the values exceed the programmed values.<a href=\"http://www.sensorsuae.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/pressure-sensor-e1450794677349.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright  wp-image-1041\" src=\"http://www.sensorsuae.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/pressure-sensor-300x250.jpg\" alt=\"pressure-sensor\" width=\"274\" height=\"228\" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>Flush mounting type display so that you can install on walls.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h4>Pressure Transmitters</h4>\r\nPSIDAC manufactuers pressure transmitters, which are used to transmite pressure data. The model number is 6280. This comes in two models, one with display and the other one without display. The model is configurable for different input and output configurations.\r\n\r\nThe pressure transmitter has models capable of measure upto2500 Pascals.',	'Vacker ties up with PSIDAC, Sweden for differential pressure sensors',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'1120-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-02-09 06:41:27',	'2016-02-09 06:41:27',	'',	1120,	'http://www.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/1120-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
