(1243,	1,	'2016-03-23 13:22:38',	'2016-03-23 13:22:38',	'<h2>Requirement of Thermal Packaging</h2><p>Thermally insulated boxes are required to store temperature sensitive items such as medicine, vaccine, blood, body cells etc. mainly for transportation. The temperature of the stored items has to be maintained within certain temperature range for time periods lasting up to couple of days and in such cases thermal packaging solutions are used.</p>',	'Passive Packaging EPS Box',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'804-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-23 13:22:38',	'2016-03-23 13:22:38',	'',	804,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/804-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1244,	1,	'2016-03-23 13:24:21',	'2016-03-23 13:24:21',	'<p>A warehouse used for storage of medicine, chemicals, food items, electronics etc. are under controlled conditions of temperature &amp; humidity. In many of these cases, it is required to record and monitor the temperature and humidity to meet regulatory requirements and internal quality assurance procedures.</p>',	'Warehouse monitoring',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'502-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-23 13:24:21',	'2016-03-23 13:24:21',	'',	502,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/502-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1245,	1,	'2016-03-23 13:32:49',	'2016-03-23 13:32:49',	'<p>Medicine refrigerators, blood refrigerators etc. need to maintain proper temperature levels to ensure proper storage of medicines, vaccines, food etc. Also Freezers used for body tissues, plasma storage, food etc. also are similar in their sensitivity.</p>',	'Refrigerator Monitoring',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'500-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-23 13:32:49',	'2016-03-23 13:32:49',	'',	500,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/500-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1246,	1,	'2016-03-23 13:34:23',	'2016-03-23 13:34:23',	'<p>Cold storage monitoring and walk in freezer monitoring are required for various temperature sensitive items such as medicines, vaccines, fruits, vegetables, fresh food, frozen food etc. which are stored under temperature controlled rooms. The storage time can be from couple of days to couple of years depending on the usage. Hence these items should never exceed permitted temperature and the conditions need to be continuously monitored and recorded. As per regulatory requirements, it might be required to check the recorded data periodically to ensure that the items have been maintained under stipulated conditions. Also nowadays insurance companies insist to have continuous recording so that they can verify upon any claims for damaged goods.</p>',	'Cold Room Monitoring',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'498-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-23 13:34:23',	'2016-03-23 13:34:23',	'',	498,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/498-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1247,	1,	'2016-03-23 13:35:39',	'2016-03-23 13:35:39',	'<p>Data centers and server rooms are the most critical system of all operations nowadays and even momentary breakdown will cause the collapse of entire operations. Hence, it is imperative that environment monitoring of data centers and server rooms are extremely important. Basically, data center monitoring has the same parameters as that of a server room monitoring and hence we are explaining both in same terms:</p>',	'Data Center Monitoring',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'496-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-23 13:35:39',	'2016-03-23 13:35:39',	'',	496,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/496-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1248,	1,	'2016-03-23 13:37:23',	'2016-03-23 13:37:23',	'<p>In hospitals, critical parameters of patient rooms need to be continuously monitored, recorded and alerts generated if required. This will be required in many cases as regulatory requirement. Such monitoring systems are required for patient rooms, Operation Theater, isolation ward etc.</p>',	'Hospital Room Monitoring',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'494-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-23 13:37:23',	'2016-03-23 13:37:23',	'',	494,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/494-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1249,	1,	'2016-03-24 04:56:38',	'2016-03-24 04:56:38',	'<p>Seemoto is the solution for all transportation and logistics companies. It provides comprehensive fleet management tools for vehicle tracking, maintenance and diagnostics as well as driver-, fuel- and safety management. It is extremely easy to install, to deploy and to use due to its technology innovations. Best of all  it supports collaboration between companies and organizations and thus enable work sharing and joint value-add. Seemoto monitors vehicles, cargo, their condition and environment - automatically and the temperature of the cargo space either on or inside the transport unit.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/seemoto-tracking-functions.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1197\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1197\" src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/seemoto-tracking-functions.png\" alt=\"seemoto tracking functions\" width=\"526\" height=\"396\" /></a></p><p>It triggers alarms and provides useful reports enhancing your business and profitability. Seemoto provides You full visibility and traceability to your supply chain and operations. Seemoto has the solution for all non-powered asset tracking needs, including trailers, containers and railway carriages.</p><h2>General benefits</h2><ul><li>Improved efficiency, both internal and external</li><li>Savings from more efficient resource usage</li><li>Improved product quality and serviceability</li><li>Increased sales and turnover</li><li>New revenue sources and business models</li></ul><p><a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/seemoto-tracking-principle.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-1198\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1198\" src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/seemoto-tracking-principle.png\" alt=\"seemoto tracking principle\" width=\"526\" height=\"396\" /></a></p>',	'Vacker ties up with Seemoto, Finland',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'1184-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 04:56:38',	'2016-03-24 04:56:38',	'',	1184,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/1184-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1250,	1,	'2016-03-24 04:57:30',	'2016-03-24 04:57:30',	'<p>PSIDAC, Sweden is a topmost manufacturer of pressure sensors, differential pressure sensors and pressure transmitters. VackerGlobal has partnered with PSIDAC for the Middle East countries. Vacker will promote their entire range of differential pressure sensors in the Middle East countries. Vacker is engaged in the following category of services.</p><ul><li>Automation for hospitals, clean rooms etc.</li><li>Supply of various sensors for industrial automation &amp; building automation.</li><li>Temperature and humidity monitoring solutions for hospitals, lifecare segment etc.</li></ul><p>As Vacker is involved in automation of critical segments, the addition of PSIDAC range of products will complement our service segment.</p><h2>Applications of differential pressure sensors</h2><p>Differential pressure sensors are used in following type of installations.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.sensorsuae.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/pressure-transmitter.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1040\" src=\"http://www.sensorsuae.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/pressure-transmitter-283x300.jpg\" alt=\"pressure-transmitter\" width=\"283\" height=\"300\" /></a></p><ul><li>Hospitals and clinics for ensuring negative pressure.</li><li>Operation theaters which need to work under controlled pressure.</li><li>Pharmaceutical manufacturing rooms, which are maintained under controlled pressure.</li><li>Isolation rooms, which are maintained under negative pressure.</li><li>Cold rooms and walk in freezers which may develop a pressure difference. This need to be monitored.</li></ul><h3>Features of Differential Pressure Sensors</h3><p>PSIDAC provides following features in the pressure sensors.</p><ul><li>The display has a touch screen for easy configuration.</li><li>The sensors can be connected to a ethernet network, BACNET protocol, MODBus etc.</li><li>An external data logger can be connected if youwsant to record data.</li><li>Visual and audible alarms if the values exceed the programmed values.<a href=\"http://www.sensorsuae.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/pressure-sensor-e1450794677349.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright  wp-image-1041\" src=\"http://www.sensorsuae.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/pressure-sensor-300x250.jpg\" alt=\"pressure-sensor\" width=\"274\" height=\"228\" /></a></li><li>Flush mounting type display so that you can install on walls.</li></ul><h4>Pressure Transmitters</h4><p>PSIDAC manufactuers pressure transmitters, which are used to transmite pressure data. The model number is 6280. This comes in two models, one with display and the other one without display. The model is configurable for different input and output configurations. The pressure transmitter has models capable of measure upto2500 Pascals.</p>',	'Vacker ties up with PSIDAC, Sweden',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'1120-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 04:57:30',	'2016-03-24 04:57:30',	'',	1120,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/1120-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1251,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:04:26',	'2016-03-24 05:04:26',	'<div class=\"post-entry\"><p>A dehumidifier is a phenomenal solution to discard excess moisture in your home or domestic environment. This helps in protecting your space from getting damaged. From the health point of view, there are many allergies which can be avoided with the help of dehumidifiers such as dust mites, mold, mildew, etc. Such allergies are more common in a humid atmosphere. Therefore a dehumidifier would be the best solution to keep yourself away from suffering from such allergies.</p><br /><p>Dehumidification is simpler and easier for smaller rooms as the capacity of humidity removal is not very high. A very uncommon situation would be to dehumidify the air in a room of approximately 400m. This is a pretty large size to dehumidify. Most of us would not prefer to have 2 to 3 dehumidifier devices kept in a single room, this might look quiet crowded. As a solution to this, we have come up with a new model which would serve the purpose by just installing one single device in a large room.</p><p>Vacker Global would like to introduce the newly launched TTK 128 E dehumidifier model. This unit is one of a kind which has a huge capacity of humidity removal. This unit is designed for larger rooms with a moisture removal capacity of up to 55 liters per day.</p><a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Large-Capacity-Dehumidifier.png\"><img src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Large-Capacity-Dehumidifier.png\" alt=\"Large Capacity Dehumidifier- Vacker Global\" width=\"351\" height=\"264\" align=\"right\" /></a><p>TTK 128 E being a large capacity based domestic dehumidifier model has an advantage of the hygrostat controlled system. This allows you to adjust the humidity level and once the same is attained, the compressor switches the unit off and ultimately saves energy.</p><p>Dehumidification is a concern in the Middle East region as the weather is mostly humid throughout the year. To be more precise, dehumidification is a concern for larger areas in the domestic sector like huge villas, museums, office space, etc. These locations would require high humidity removal capacity due to which we have come up with the TTK 128 E which can dehumidify an area of up to 160 meter square.</p><a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Domestic-Type-Dehumidifier.png\"><img src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Domestic-Type-Dehumidifier.png\" alt=\"Domestic Type Dehumidifier VackerGlobal\" width=\"351\" height=\"264\" align=\"right\" /></a><p>This domestic dehumidifier has a two stage blower and has an easy methodology in handling the unit which provides a timer through which the operating time can be controlled.</p><p>Normally the manual draining of the water tank in such units would be difficult on a periodic basis. As a solution to this problem the TTK 128 E comes with a separate hose which can drain out the condensed water automatically. Also to add on another feature of the unit, the TTK 128 E has a warning light which is lit whenever the tank is full. This helps indicate that the water needs to be discarded. At such times, the unit would be in the sleep mode until the tank is not empty.</p><p>With regards to the applications for dehumidifiers for large areas, it is better to have a single unit of high capacity like the TTK 128 E. Many a times there are rooms interconnected within a house which are open to each other. In such cases a high capacity based unit would suffice the problem.</p><a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Comfort-Condensation-Type-Dehumidifier.png\"><img src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Comfort-Condensation-Type-Dehumidifier.png\" alt=\"Comfort Condensation Type Dehumidifier\" width=\"351\" height=\"264\" align=\"right\" /></a><p>To conclude with, the TTK 128 E has an operating range for temperature between 5 to 32C and an operating range for humidity between 30 to 90%. This range would cover most of the natural routine scenarios. Also the sound level of the machine is approximately around 56 dB.</p><p><b>Note:</b> For your understanding, a table fan would produce a sound level of 45 dB.</p></div>',	'New model dehumidifier TTK-128E launched',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'746-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:04:26',	'2016-03-24 05:04:26',	'',	746,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/746-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1252,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:12:02',	'2016-03-24 05:12:02',	'<p>Temperature mapping study and Temperature qualification study are carried out generally in pharmaceutical industry.undefined There are different kind of medicines and vaccines which need to be stored and transported at certain temperatures. Majority of these medicines and vaccines are under two categories viz. Those to be stored between 2 to 8 Degree Centigrade and those to be stored between 15 to 25C. It is important for the efficacy of the medicine that the same be stored and transported at the recommended temperature limits as above. If the medicine or vaccine goes above these temperature limits, the medicinal properties will be gradually lost and most importantly the products will not show any indication that it has been compromised. In such case the ultimate distributor and user will be unaware of the efficacy of the medicine. The storage is done in warehouses, cold rooms or refrigerators and transportation is carried out in boxes, vans, reefers and containers. The whole set of study is carried out to analyze the temperature distribution in a warehouse, cold room, refrigerator, van or reefer trucks to find out whether the temperature inside such facility is always maintained between the desired temperature</p>',	'Temperature Mapping Study & Temperature Qualification Study',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'426-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:12:02',	'2016-03-24 05:12:02',	'',	426,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/426-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1253,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:13:19',	'2016-03-24 05:13:19',	'<p class=\"text-para\">A software will be installed on the mobile phone which will continuously check and transmit various parameters of the vehicle. The present day systems involve fixing a device in the car which is completely eliminated in our system. We need just to install the software on any compatible mobile phone and the data can be viewed either on the mobile or through the website. The charges involve just one time charges and very nominal yearly charges for the server space. Salient features are:</p><ul><li>Features accessible through Mobile App</li><li>Live Tracking</li><li>Replay</li><li>Transit Report</li><li>Features Accessible through Web</li><li>Access control</li><li>Report</li><li>Supported Platforms for Mobile</li><li>Analytics</li><li>Android version 2.2</li><li>Symbian 3</li></ul>',	'Vehicle tracking through the mobile phone of the driver',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'424-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:13:19',	'2016-03-24 05:13:19',	'',	424,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/424-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1254,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:14:18',	'2016-03-24 05:14:18',	'<p>The temperature of the medicine storage room has to be maintained between 2 -8 Deg Celsius. Our system recently installed at a storage facility in Kuwait continuously monitors and records the temperature of the room. In case the temperature goes below 2 Deg Celsius or goes above 8 Deg Celsius for 5 minutes (the duration and the temperature range can be changed), an automated phone call is made up to 4 operators to inform the alarm condition. The phone calls are repeated until one of them attends and acknowledges the phone. The data can be stored in a computer and can be viewed through internet also from any part of the world.</p><h2>These instruments can be fitted for any temperature controlled rooms such as Blood Storage Rooms, Food Storage rooms etc.</h2>',	'Temperature monitoring & Alarm device installed at a medicine storage cold room',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'422-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:14:18',	'2016-03-24 05:14:18',	'',	422,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/422-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1255,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:15:07',	'2016-03-24 05:15:07',	'<p>4 nos. existing class rooms at Indian Community School , Kuwait were converted into sophisticated laboratories (Chemistry, Biology, Physics &amp; Computer labs). The labs were completed in a record time of 45 days.</p><h1>The labs have the following automated features for energy conservation:</h1><ul><li>Light, Fan, AC etc. are automated to work only when children are present in the room.</li><li>The AC of computer lab is automated so that when students are not present, ACs will work alternatively for 12 hours each to keep the temperature under control. When students are present both ACs will work simultaneously to maintain the room temperature.</li><li>Gas leakage is automatically detected and the system shuts off in case of a leakage.</li><li>Even If the children leave the room with the burners in ON condition, gas will be shut OFF after everyone leaves the room.</li></ul>',	'Sophisticated new academic Laboratories done for a School at Kuwait',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'420-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:15:07',	'2016-03-24 05:15:07',	'',	420,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/420-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1256,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:17:26',	'2016-03-24 05:17:26',	'<p class=\"text-para\">The Hybrid Security Management Solutions being offered by DEVENIO-IS has the unique advantage that existing hardware need not be replaced and the solutions can be easily integrated into existing security surveillance cameras and access control systems. Few of the prominent capabilities are</p><ul><li>Integration with various cameras such as IR, thermal, Analogue, HD, IP etc</li><li>People and vehicles counting</li><li>Unattended object detection</li><li>Queue length detection</li><li>Intrusion detection which can exclude dogs, birds etc</li><li>No need to change existing hardware</li><li>Integrate thousands of cameras</li><li>Incorporate access control, fire detection or burglar alarm systems etc. into single software</li><li>Record and store any number plate of a vehicle entering or leaving</li></ul>',	'Dealer of Devenio IS in UAE, Kuwait, Oman and India',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'418-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:17:26',	'2016-03-24 05:17:26',	'',	418,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/418-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1257,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:18:44',	'2016-03-24 05:18:44',	'<p class=\"text-para\">We have installed a complete solution to monitor all possible parameters of a data center and in case any of the parameters exceed the defined limits, a phone call will be made to 4 technicians and a voice mail will be delivered indicating the nature of the fault. Also SMS and emails will be sent simultaneously. The various parameters monitored are:</p><ul class=\"twolink\"><li>Temperature</li><li>Humidity</li><li>Air Flow</li><li>Water Leaks</li><li>Status of all doors of racks</li><li>Main Door Status</li><li>Power Failure</li><li>Excess Ampere</li><li>Excess Ampere</li><li>Voltage monitoring</li><li>Battery Condition</li></ul><p class=\"text-para\">All the above parameters will be continuously monitored and recorded in a central computer. A qualified technician was stationed round the clock in the data center. However after installing our integrated solution, the technician is not required and the system is working as expected for past 3 months.</p>',	'Data Centre Monitoring Project done in kuwait',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'416-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:18:44',	'2016-03-24 05:18:44',	'',	416,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/416-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1258,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:19:40',	'2016-03-24 05:19:40',	'<p class=\"text-para\">We have carried out a temperature mapping &amp; validation of a massive pharmaceutical warehouse in Uae. The warehouse is more than 200,000 sq. ft in size and is having hundreds of racks. Even though theoretically we can carry out mapping on part by part basis, it will not give exact details in view of various operating conditions. Hence we took data simultaneously using hundreds of data loggers simultaneously and was validated through our international partners.</p><p class=\"text-para\">A complete 3D imaging also is done so as to carry out the once again during winter.</p>',	'Temperature mapping of warehouse done in UAE',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'414-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:19:40',	'2016-03-24 05:19:40',	'',	414,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/414-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1259,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:24:10',	'2016-03-24 05:24:10',	'<p>Vacker Group of companies is established to provide specialized engineering solutions with a focus on energy conservation and are presently involved in Industrial/Process automation, Home/Office automation, MEP contracting, engineering activities and Trading in Electro-Mechanical items.</p>',	'About Company',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'59-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:24:10',	'2016-03-24 05:24:10',	'',	59,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/59-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1260,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:25:22',	'2016-03-24 05:25:22',	'<p>Dehumidifiers are used for removing moisture from air. The moisture content in air is known as humidity. This is measured in Relative Humidity as a percentage. This is calculated as a percentage of the air volume. For a living environment, the ideal humidity level is between 45% to 65%.</p><p><br /><a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Commercial-Dehumidifier-TTK800.png\"><img src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Commercial-Dehumidifier-TTK800.png\" alt=\"Commercial Dehumidifier TTK800 VackerGlobal\" width=\"351\" height=\"264\" align=\"right\" /></a></p><p>If the humidity is above 65%, a dehumidifer has to be used. If the level goes below or above these levels, it is not comfortable for human beings. Also it may cause adverse health effects. Dehumidifiers are classified based on the technology such as refrigeration and desiccant. Also they are classified based on its usage.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Dehumidifers are used for different applications.These include home, office, warehouse, cold room, basement etc. Based on the application, corresponding terminology is used. Eg. A dehumidifer used in cold room is known as cold room dehumidifier. Similarly those used in a warehouse is known as warehouse dehumidifier.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We are supplying various dehumidifiers manufactured by Trotec, Germany. Trotec is manufacturing dehumidifiers ranging from 8 liter per day to 2000 liter per day. Explosion proof models of dehumidifiers also are manufactured for such environments. Also for heavy duty applications, the casing will be stainless steel.</p><p><br /> <a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/contact-us/\"><img src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Contact-us.png\" alt=\"Contact us VackerGlobal\" width=\"150\" height=\"60\" align=\"center\" /></a></p>',	'Dehumidifier & Humidifier',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'55-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:25:22',	'2016-03-24 05:25:22',	'',	55,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/55-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1261,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:27:11',	'2016-03-24 05:27:11',	'<p>VackerGlobal is leading automation company and system integrator, providing numerous custom made solutions. Automation is carried in various applications for commercial and residential applications.</p><h2>Automation company</h2><p>As an Automation company, few of our major fields of automation are listed below.</p><ul><ul><li>Building Automation for automated building solutions.</li></ul></ul><p><a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Automation-company-Dubai.png\"><img src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Automation-company-Dubai.png\" alt=\"Automation Company Dubai Vacker Global\" width=\"351\" height=\"264\" align=\"right\" /></a></p><ul><ul><li>Industrial Automation for machineries.</li><li>Process Automation for automating industrial processes.</li><li>PLC Automation, which uses Programmable Logic Controllers (PLC).</li><li>Hospital automation for various monitoring instruments in Hospitals.</li><li>BACNet Automation, which use BACNet protocol for communication.</li><li>KNX Automation for KNX type of protocols.</li><li>Modbus Automation for protocols through Modbus.</li><li>Marine Automation for marine projects, ships etc.</li></ul></ul><p><br /><a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/System-integrator-Dubai-UAE.png\"><img src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/System-integrator-Dubai-UAE.png\" alt=\"System Integration Dubai UAE\" width=\"351\" height=\"264\" align=\"right\" /></a></p><p>We have 5 years of experience as an Automation company in Dubai undertaking various such projects.</p><h2>System Integrator</h2><p>We are one of the foremost system integrators in Dubai, UAE. Our Dubai office is an approved system Integrator for various manufacturers.</p><p>System integrator is a terminology used for Automation companies. This involves design, installation and commissioning of automation projects.</p><p>The components will be supplied to a system integrator by manufacturers such as Beckhoff, GFR, Allen Bradley, Emerson, SIEMENS, Rockwell, ABB etc.</p><p>As a system integrator, we have trained personnel from Beckhoff, GFR, Allen Bradley etc. We design automation projects using such components and execute projects.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/automation-company-Dubai-UAE.png\"><img src=\"http://www.vackerglobal.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/automation-company-Dubai-UAE.png\" alt=\"Automation Company Dubai VackerGlobal\" width=\"351\" height=\"264\" align=\"right\" /></a></p><p>Our scope will include complete design, panel building, wiring, installation, testing &amp; commissioning. Different manufacturers have their own programming software. Also, communication protocols will be different for each of them.</p><p>A solution will need numerous components interlinked to each other. A project can be defined by different experts in different methods. The expertise of a system integration company is to find out the most economic and technically correct design.</p><p>We also develop the required software for the specific project. This can be done using the development platform of the manufacturer. Also. custom software can be developed to integrate to the manufacturers software.</p>',	'Automation',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'49-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:27:11',	'2016-03-24 05:27:11',	'',	49,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/49-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1262,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:27:55',	'2016-03-24 05:27:55',	'<p>A data logger is a machine equipped with a sensor, an electronic chip, and internal memory designed to record data at regular intervals for detailed analysis in the future. The sensor measures the physical phenomena or the source of data. The data collected by the sensor is converted into electronic signals by the chip, which then proceeds to store the information in its internal memory. A data interface mechanism allows the logged data to be accessed for analysis and interpretation.</p><p>A data logger is a versatile device that can be used for a wide range of reasons. From assessing the amount of sunlight or rain received by a city or region to the average temperature of the cold storage vehicle throughout its journey across the countrya data logger facilitates automatic collection of data at periodic intervals without any reliability or performance issues. Two commonly-used data loggers are devices that measure and log temperature and humidity.</p>',	'Data Loggers',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'46-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:27:55',	'2016-03-24 05:27:55',	'',	46,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/46-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1263,	1,	'2016-03-24 05:28:20',	'2016-03-24 05:28:20',	'<p>The term Cold Chain is referred to temperature sensitive goods. These include medicine, vaccine, frozen food, blood storage, body tissues etc. To a lesser extent these are also applicable for fruits, vegetables, flowers etc. which also need to be under controlled temperature conditions.</p><p>The cold chain represents the chain of activities throughout the entire chain of handling the product. This will cover production, packing, storage, global transportation, local storage, warehousing, last mile transportation etc. Cold Chain Management implies that the temperature need to be managed across entire duration.</p><p>Cold Chain Management solutions includes every product and solution that is required to maintain and monitor the temperature. These will include monitoring systems, packaging solutions, testing of various items etc.</p>',	'Cold Chain Management',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'43-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-03-24 05:28:20',	'2016-03-24 05:28:20',	'',	43,	'http://en-ke.vackerglobal.com/uncategorized/43-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
